          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The faculty is the the most likeable as they are very supportive.",
          "name": "Aastha Jha",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech"
        },
        {
          "text": "The quality of infrastructure is not that good but they provide us adequate facilities. Such as Ac, wifi , Drinking water, washrooms, security, parking ,stationary.",
          "name": "Aditya singj",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Tech {Lateral}"
        },
        {
          "text": "As i know that every student got a good placement who concentrated in his/her studies. There is also a entrepreneurship cell in our college also.",
